verses.verse: Praise <WH1984> Yah! <WH3050> Praise <WH1984> God <WH410> in his sanctuary! <WH6944> Praise <WH1984> him in his heavens <WH7549> for his acts of power! <WH5797>
Praise <WH1984> him for his mighty acts! <WH1369> Praise <WH1984> him according to his excellent <WH7230> greatness! <WH1433>
Praise <WH1984> him with the sounding <WH8629> of the trumpet! <WH7782> Praise <WH1984> him with harp <WH5035> and lyre! <WH5035>
Praise <WH1984> him with tambourine <WH8596> and dancing! <WH4234> Praise <WH1984> him with stringed instruments <WH4482> and flute! <WH5748>
Praise <WH1984> him with loud <WH8088> cymbals! <WH6767> Praise <WH1984> him with resounding <WH8643> cymbals! <WH6767>
Let everything that has breath <WH5397> praise <WH1984> Yah! <WH3050> Praise <WH1984> Yah! <WH3050>
